{"tid":1278123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七一嘅煲底討論反思","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:58:55.000Z","uid":92230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"feadcc1e04dad22e41252bcffed94b05a5fc14c2","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"發夢去到煲底討論升級<br />\n有人喺旗杆下set咪大家輪流講嘢<br />\n最後表決時間地點<br />\n有兩點我覺得擔心<br />\n<br />\n第一 表決時間嘅時候 在場大部分人都叫緊即時行動唔好等遊行隊頭 但揸咪條友淨係俾人揀三點 四點 五點 最後無人理個表決 起身即刻行動<br />\n<br />\n第二 民主討論完表決完行動緊 有人又拎咪話唔好送死之類 想重啟討論 呢啲人喺現場係做後援嘅 就唔喺度點名了<br />\n<br />\n我覺得出到嚟嘅示威者都好高質 <br />\n所以諗唔明點解呢班示威者之間嘅民主過程會咁樣<br />\n有無人解答下<br />\n<br />\n利申 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非分化 非指責</span> 真心問"},{"pid":"79cfe5223a9aea2a2d4d807afe168394d69389e5","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"諗極都唔明大家點解咁樣<br />\n好彩現場人士大叫 各有各做<br />\n行動先無被腰斬"},{"pid":"874462b7dbef0d9143cee4dfe518bc71a9b43850","tid":1278123,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"都各有各做<br />\n表決黎做乜"},{"pid":"40c94c57845ca64721fd4ca06aa768c07237119a","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"但討論完又叫人唔好衝果下真係有少少打擊士氣"},{"pid":"d5d194d96091d901f406bede083a144d2b349ab3","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874462b7dbef0d9143cee4dfe518bc71a9b43850","tid":1278123,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"都各有各做<br />\n表決黎做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"要夠人 所以先一齊討論同表決"},{"pid":"d92bbae6cabd368221118e7b9891910f7b796374","tid":1278123,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874462b7dbef0d9143cee4dfe518bc71a9b43850","tid":1278123,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"都各有各做<br />\n表決黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"咁都要顧下手足安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係各有各做就唔使同人講同討論"},{"pid":"3ac524793317c7bf3acd75dd11f9dd456f3e09ee","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"以為出得嚟 甚至留埋夜嘅人 應該都係勇武喇掛<br />\n原來勇武中間都仲可以分程度"},{"pid":"3bd0e17615e5f4c8ba4acf67e118327d81116eb5","tid":1278123,"uid":193346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"其實要討論既野應該係點樣衝<br />\n而唔係衝唔衝<br />\n咁樣既話其實對義士先會比較安全"},{"pid":"694109e4467a9efdc1a0e5105d4db1e4cbf25eba","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"有無發夢夢見煲底嘅人可以入嚟討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaf857707e416ba85347a8bd2a97a60eb65c4d4","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bd0e17615e5f4c8ba4acf67e118327d81116eb5","tid":1278123,"uid":193346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"其實要討論既野應該係點樣衝<br />\n而唔係衝唔衝<br />\n咁樣既話其實對義士先會比較安全"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"但現場後援係傾向唔衝<br />\n雖然佢地無好似梁耀忠咁阻人"},{"pid":"4a1c5e4785babdede7b54cf53de86fc05b9ba4e0","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"有無人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff92cbfafae7991881780ce9737045c3831e4d00","tid":1278123,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a30ee05cd87f0eb2033a608e37d37bddf51897","tid":1278123,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5d194d96091d901f406b